om/2019/10/jonah-hill-no-longer-circling-the-batman-1202760771/ |archive-date=October 16, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PattinsonPay\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2480930/how-much-robert-pattinson-is-reportedly-making-for-the-batman |title=How Much Robert Pattinson Is Reportedly Making For 'The Batman' |last=Evans |first=Nick |website=CinemaBlend |date=September 25, 2019 |access-date=October 17, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190926235456/https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2480930/how-much-robert-pattinson-is-reportedly-making-for-the-batman |archive-date=September 26, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"FarrellTalks\">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/11/colin-farrell-the-penguin-batman-movie-cast-1202766532/ |title=Colin Farrell In Talks To Play Penguin, Rounding Out 'The Batman' Villain Trio |last=Fleming Jr. |first=Mike |work=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |date=November 5, 2019 |access-date=November 5, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191105215438/https://deadline.com/2019/11/colin-farrell-the-penguin-batman-movie-cast-1202766532/ |archive-date=November 5, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<!-- FILMING -->\n\n<ref name=\"SlashFilmJan2020\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.slashfilm.com/the-batman-has-begun-filming/ |title=Criminals of Gotham, Beware: 'The Batman' Has Begun Filming |last=Pearson |first=Ben |work=[[/Film]] |date=January 6, 2020 |access-date=January 7, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200107145244/https://www.slashfilm.com/the-batman-has-begun-filming/ |archive-date=January 7, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ScreenRantJan2020\">{{Cite web |url=https://screenrant.com/batman-movie-jeffery-wright-commissioner-gordon-gotham-filming/ |title='The Batman's Commissioner Gordon, Jeffery Wright, Announces Start of Filming |website=[[Screen Rant]] |last=Ross |first=Diandra |date=January 5, 2020 |accessdate=January 6, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/